      "writtenOn": "2018-10-11T14:10:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Different usages of the framework could have additional flags. Is that correct?\n\nIf this is \"Required flags for all TaskDrivers\" should it be defined in a common place like common_flags.go / required_flags.go or something like that? MustInit and basic.go could then be documented to mention it.",
