        "id": 5145
      },
      "writtenOn": "2018-10-12T14:36:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "We got around the problem of having to repeatedly define common flags in CT by keeping them in master_common.go and worker_common.go. I can also see the advantage of having them visible at the top. Probably comes down to personal preference.\nMaybe leave this section and also add below:\n// Optional flags go here (if required)\n\nCan also add a sample optional flag. Or leave it blank.",
      "parentUuid": "e00957eb_5a3f5eb2",
