      "writtenOn": "2018-10-11T14:25:16Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The step is just anonymous in that case.  Unlike in recipes, where the name is the ID of the step (which caused all kinds of problems, eg. names have to be unique and URL-safe or their logs disappear), IMO names should be optional for simple steps.",
      "parentUuid": "197e4525_355dbf5f",
